<p>Friday, 07 February 2020</p>
<p>“Education is what, when, and why to do things. Training is how to do it.</p>
<p>“In science, if you know what you are doing, you should not be doing it. In engineering, if you do not know what you are doing, you should not be doing it.”—Richard Hamming, <em>The Art of Doing Science and Engineering</em> (1997)</p>
